# ===================================================================
# physical-ai-stl — repository .gitignore
# Purpose: keep commits lean, reproducible, and CI-friendly while avoiding
#          accidental commits of large data, experiment artifacts, secrets,
#          or local editor/system files.
# ===================================================================
#
# House rules:
#   • Never ignore source/config: keep src/**, scripts/**, configs/**, tests/**, docs/** (except build outputs).
#   • Commit only *small* curated artifacts (figures, tiny demo assets, summary tables); keep raw run outputs out of git.
#   • Secrets live only in .env / key stores; examples are kept as *.env.example.
#
########################
# 1) Python essentials #
########################
# Byte-compiled / cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Compiled extensions
*.so
*.pyd
*.dylib
cython_debug/

